{"ID":"20260605111825-cwwwgnd","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260605111825-cwwwgnd","title":"2021年天津卷","type":"doc","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605111825-rtq6x0u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111825-rtq6x0u","updated":"20260605111429"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"夫儒生，礼义也；耕战，饮食也。贵耕战而贱儒生，是弃礼义求饮食也。使礼义废，纲纪败，上下乱而阴阳谬，水旱失时，五谷不登，万民饥死，农不得耕，士不得战也。故以旧防为无益而去之，必有水灾；以旧礼为无补而去之，必有乱患。儒者之在世，礼义之旧防也，有之无益，无之有损。夫礼义，无成效于人，然成效者须"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sup","TextMarkTextContent":"[1]"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"礼义而成。犹足蹈路而行，所路之路须不蹈者；身须手足而动，动者待不动者。故事或无益，而益者须之；或无效，而效者待之。儒生，耕战所须待也，弃而不存，如何？"}]},{"ID":"20260605111825-6v3qyy3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111825-6v3qyy3","updated":"20260605111429"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"韩子非儒，谓之无益有损，盖谓俗儒无行操，举措不重礼，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"以儒名而俗行"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，以实学而伪说，贪官尊荣，故不足贵。夫志洁行显，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"不徇爵禄"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，去卿相之位若脱躧者，居位治职，功虽不立，此礼义为业者也。国之所以存者，礼义也。民无礼义，倾国危主。今儒者之操，重礼爱义，率无礼义士，激无义之人。人民为善，爱其主上，此亦有益也。闻伯夷风者，贪夫廉，懦夫有立志；闻柳下惠风者，薄夫敦，鄙夫宽。"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"此上化也，非人所见。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111825-65kzgoz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111825-65kzgoz","updated":"20260605111429"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"段干木"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sup","TextMarkTextContent":"【2】"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"阖门不出，魏文"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sup","TextMarkTextContent":"【3】"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"敬之，表式其闾，秦军闻之，卒不攻魏。使魏无干木，秦兵入境，境土危亡。秦，强国也，兵无不胜，兵加于魏，魏国必破，三军兵顿，流血千里。今魏文式阖门之士，却强秦之兵，全魏国之境，济三军之众，功莫大焉，赏莫先焉。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111825-5n3dzdb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111825-5n3dzdb","updated":"20260605111429"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"齐有高节之士，曰狂谲、华士，二人昆弟也，义不降志，不仕非其主。太公封于齐，以此二子解沮"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"sup","TextMarkTextContent":"【4】"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"齐众，开不为上用之路，同时诛之。韩子善之，以为二子无益而有损也。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111825-8nyc4v4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111825-8nyc4v4","updated":"20260605111429"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"夫狂谲、华士，段干木之类也，太公诛之，无所却到；魏文侯式之，却强秦而全魏，功孰大者？狂谲、华士之操，干木之节也，使韩子善干木阖门之节、高魏文之式是也，则善太公之诛非也。使韩子"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"非干木之行，下魏文之式"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，则干木以此行而有益，魏文用式之道为有功；是韩子不赏功、尊有益也。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111825-8f2df5y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111825-8f2df5y","updated":"20260605111429"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（取材于王充《论衡·非韩》）"}]},{"ID":"20260605111825-as2sbe2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111825-as2sbe2","updated":"20260605111429"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"注释：【1】须：等待，这里是依靠的意思。【2】段干木：战国时魏国隐士。【3】魏文：魏文候，战国初魏国君主。【4】解沮：瓦解、涣散。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111839-adxllcu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111839-adxllcu","updated":"20260605111839"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"世之所谓智者，知天下之利害，而审乎计之得失，如斯而已矣。此其为智犹有所穷。唯见天下之利而为之，唯其害而不为，则是有时而穷焉，亦不能尽天下之利。古之所谓大智者，知天下利害得失之计，而权之以人。是故有所犯天下之至危而卒以成大功者，此以其人权之。轻敌者败，重敌者无成功。何者？天下未尝有百全之利也，举事而待其百全，则必有所格，是故知吾之所以胜人，而人不知其所以胜我者，天下莫能敌之。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111839-u6cqmbg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111839-u6cqmbg","updated":"20260605111839"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当汉氏之衰，豪杰并起而图天下，二袁、董、吕争为强暴，而孙权、刘备又已区区于一隅，其用兵制胜，固不足以敌曹氏，然天下终于分裂，讫魏之世，而不能一。盖尝试论之。魏武长于料事，而不长于料人。刘备有盖世之才，而无应卒之机。方其新破刘璋，蜀人未附，一日而四五惊，斩之不能禁。释此时不取，而其后遂至于不敢加兵者终其身。孙权勇而有谋，此不可以声势恐喝取也。魏武不用中原之长，而与之争于舟楫之间，一日一夜，行三百里以争利。"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"犯此二败以攻孙权，是以丧师于赤壁，以成吴之强。"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"且夫刘备可以急取，而不可以缓图。方其危疑之间，卷甲而趋之，虽兵法之所忌，可以得志。孙权者，可以计取，而不可以势破也，而欲以荆州新附之卒，乘胜而取之。彼非不知其难，特欲侥幸于权之不敢抗也。此用之于新造之蜀，乃可以逞。故夫魏武重发于刘备而丧其功，轻为于孙权而至于败。"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"此不亦长于料事而不长于料人之过欤"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"？"}]},{"ID":"20260605111839-r01aid1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111839-r01aid1","updated":"20260605111839"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"嗟夫！事之利害，计之得失，天下之能者举知之。"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"知之而不能权之以人则亦纷纷焉或胜或负争为雄强而未见其能一也。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111839-fyr352b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111839-fyr352b","updated":"20260605111839"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（宋·苏轼《魏武帝论》，有删节）"}]},{"ID":"20260605111839-zdimxb5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111839-zdimxb5","updated":"20260605111839"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"观曹公明锐权略，神变不穷，兵折而意不衰，在危而听不惑，临事决机，举无遗悔，近古以来，未之有也。虽复名微众寡，地小力穷，官渡受围，濮阳战屈。然天下精明之士，拓落之材，趋若百川之崇巨海，游尘之集高岳。故有荀彧、郭嘉等，或敛风长感，或一见尽怀。然后览英雄之心，骋熊罴之勇，挟天子以崇大顺，扶幼主而显至公，武功赫然，霸业成矣。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111839-w6biok9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111839-w6biok9","updated":"20260605111839"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（唐·朱敬则《魏武帝论》，有删节）"}]},{"ID":"20260605111825-o7xvw0g","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605111825-o7xvw0g","updated":"20260605111853"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题目"}]},{"ID":"20260605111853-r5azykk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111853-r5azykk","updated":"20260605111853"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"7．对下列各句中加点词的解释，不正确的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260605111853-3elaa2j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111853-3elaa2j","updated":"20260605111853"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．而审乎计之得失         审：仔细考量"}]},{"ID":"20260605111853-35qy4ni","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111853-35qy4ni","updated":"20260605111853"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．则必有所格             格：阻止，阻碍"}]},{"ID":"20260605111853-s2e9w78","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111853-s2e9w78","updated":"20260605111853"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．此用之于新造之蜀       造：拜访"}]},{"ID":"20260605111853-4382wxc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111853-4382wxc","updated":"20260605111853"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．或一见尽怀             或：有的人"}]},{"ID":"20260605111853-e958uwz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111853-e958uwz","updated":"20260605111853"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"8．下列各句中加点词的意义和用法，相同的一组是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260605111853-nxky5q4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111853-nxky5q4","updated":"20260605111853"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．则是有时而穷焉            盘盘焉，囷囷焉"}]},{"ID":"20260605111853-e8u1jjy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111853-e8u1jjy","updated":"20260605111853"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．而权之以人                臣以供养无主，辞不赴命"}]},{"ID":"20260605111853-lu5th12","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111853-lu5th12","updated":"20260605111853"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．特欲侥幸于权之不敢抗也    臣诚恐见欺于王而负赵"}]},{"ID":"20260605111853-q32p2df","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111853-q32p2df","updated":"20260605111853"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．游尘之集高岳              不知东方之既白"}]},{"ID":"20260605111853-d80oalj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111853-d80oalj","updated":"20260605111853"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"9．文中画波浪线的句子，断句最合理的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260605111853-q08pamo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111853-q08pamo","updated":"20260605111853"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．知之而不能权之/以人则亦纷纷焉/或胜或负/争为雄强而未见/其能一也"}]},{"ID":"20260605111853-gnw074u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111853-gnw074u","updated":"20260605111853"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．知之而不能权之以人/则亦纷纷焉或胜或负/争为雄强/而未见其能一也"}]},{"ID":"20260605111853-osnrdcv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111853-osnrdcv","updated":"20260605111853"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．知之而不能/权之以人则亦纷纷焉/或胜或负争为雄强/而未见其能一也"}]},{"ID":"20260605111853-rxvg9bb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111853-rxvg9bb","updated":"20260605111853"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．知之/而不能权之以人/则亦纷纷焉或胜/或负争为雄强而未见/其能一也"}]},{"ID":"20260605111853-k6yckej","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111853-k6yckej","updated":"20260605111853"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"10．下列六句分编四组，都属于苏轼认为曹操应该采取的正确做法的一组是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260605111853-7w2c5d8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111853-7w2c5d8","updated":"20260605111853"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"①孙权勇而有谋，此不可以声势恐喝取也       ②与之争于舟楫之间"}]},{"ID":"20260605111853-oc714kv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111853-oc714kv","updated":"20260605111853"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"③行三百里以争利                           ④刘备可以急取，而不可以缓图"}]},{"ID":"20260605111853-zvpxc3n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111853-zvpxc3n","updated":"20260605111853"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"⑤方其危疑之间，卷甲而趋之                 ⑥欲以荆州新附之卒，乘胜而取之"}]},{"ID":"20260605111853-1sm7b88","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111853-1sm7b88","updated":"20260605111853"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．①③⑥                    B．①④⑤                    C．②③④                    D．②⑤⑥"}]},{"ID":"20260605111853-o8m2on3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111853-o8m2on3","updated":"20260605111853"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"11．下列对选文的理解与分析，不恰当的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260605111853-ap4rx9i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111853-ap4rx9i","updated":"20260605111853"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．苏轼一开篇就肯定了明辨利害即为“智者”的看法，并认为“大智者”还必须善于权衡对手。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111853-o0ayjqt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111853-o0ayjqt","updated":"20260605111853"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．苏轼认为曹操过于重视刘备、又过于轻视孙权，因而错失统一的时机。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111853-g760go6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111853-g760go6","updated":"20260605111853"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．朱敬则认为曹操在名望、实力上不占优势，又屡次战败，但最终扶持幼主，使朝廷稳定。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111853-gukliet","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111853-gukliet","updated":"20260605111853"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．两则选文摆事实、讲道理，观点鲜明，条理清晰，文气充沛，很有说服力。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111853-9kpy7s9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111853-9kpy7s9","updated":"20260605111853"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"12．把文言文阅读材料中画横线的句子翻译成现代汉语。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111853-7i2j02w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111853-7i2j02w","updated":"20260605111853"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（1）犯此二败以攻孙权，是以丧师于赤壁，以成吴之强。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111853-7zjxe1a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111853-7zjxe1a","updated":"20260605111853"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（2）此不亦长于料事而不长于料人之过欤？"}]},{"ID":"20260605111853-ysk4xde","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111853-ysk4xde","updated":"20260605111853"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"13．请用自己的话概括苏轼和朱敬则对曹操评价的不同之处。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111825-hrg3q98","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605111825-hrg3q98","updated":"20260605111908"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案"}]},{"ID":"20260605111908-gi1y4oa","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111908-gi1y4oa","updated":"20260605111908"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"7．C    8．D    9．B    10．B    11．A    12．（1）犯了这两个（导致失败的）错误来攻打孙权，因此在赤壁兵败，成就了孙吴的强大。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111908-hial1mp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111908-hial1mp","updated":"20260605111908"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（2）这不也就是擅长揣度事情却不擅长揣度他人（所造成）的过错吗？    13．①苏轼认为曹操不是“大智者”，他不能准确地权衡对手，未能统一天下。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111908-86q40pe","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111908-86q40pe","updated":"20260605111908"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"②朱敬则高度肯定了曹操的功业，认为曹操有谋略，善决断，意志坚定，以至吸引贤才归附，成就霸业。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111825-2xsucp7","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605111825-2xsucp7","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解析"}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-m1tmuuc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-m1tmuuc","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"7．本题考查学生理解文言实词在文中的意义和用法的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-q0rbxuf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-q0rbxuf","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C.句意：这种做法，用在刘备刚刚占领的西蜀。造：到达、占领。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-ohve49b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-ohve49b","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选C。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-xduqp8k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-xduqp8k","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"8．本题考查学生理解文言虚词在文中的意义和用法的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-115elqk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-115elqk","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A.句末语气词，可译为“了”或不译；形容词词尾，……的样子；"}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-gtlejju","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-gtlejju","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B.介词，根据；连词，因为；"}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-sbex4ta","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-sbex4ta","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C.介词，在；介词，表被动；"}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-gmh0udk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-gmh0udk","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D.两个都是助词，主谓之间取消句子独立性。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-4q5e3ad","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-4q5e3ad","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选D。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-oc1kke9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-oc1kke9","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"9．本题考查学生文言文断句的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-50vj6th","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-50vj6th","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"句子大意是：但仅仅知道这个，不能根据人的特点来斟酌使用，所以魏武帝有时胜，有时败，争雄一生，却没有看到他统一天下。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-052eoxo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-052eoxo","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“权之以人”是介词结构后置句，不能断开，排除A；"}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-anrad9b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-anrad9b","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“则”一般用于句首，其前断开，排除C；"}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-wqpqfgl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-wqpqfgl","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“而”一般用于句首，其前断开，排除D。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-07cdidk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-07cdidk","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选B。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-7t6md3l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-7t6md3l","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"10．本题考查学生对文章内容的分析理解能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-0e2rji1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-0e2rji1","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"②是说曹操不利用中原地区的优势，却用水军与孙权一决雌雄，属于错误做法，不符合题干要求；"}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-tw41ni6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-tw41ni6","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"③是说曹操一日一夜行军三百里前去争利，犯了兵家大忌，是错误做法，不符合题干要求；"}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-85nokfy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-85nokfy","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"⑥是说孙权，应以计谋巧取，不能用人多势众来强攻，曹操却想用刚刚投降的荆州士兵，乘胜拿下孙权，这是错误做法，不符合题干要求。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-bdmu287","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-bdmu287","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"排除这三个选项。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-19gd4nk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-19gd4nk","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选B。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-nud8mvs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-nud8mvs","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"11．本题考查学生对选文的理解与分析能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-wcp5r54","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-wcp5r54","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A.“肯定了明辨利害即为‘智者’的看法”错。结合原文“世之所谓智者，知天下之利害，而审乎计之得失，如斯而已矣。此其为智犹有所穷”，可见作者并不认为仅仅明辨利害就是“智者”。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-njqg1tb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-njqg1tb","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选A。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-4xdzqxk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-4xdzqxk","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"12．本题考查学生理解并翻译文言文句子的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-ftpp7bt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-ftpp7bt","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（1）题得分点有：败，错误；是以，因此；成，成就。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-p0irib6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-p0irib6","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（2）题得分点有：不亦……欤，不也就是……吗；料，揣度。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-i7atsxm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-i7atsxm","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"13．本题考查学生评价探究作者思想观点的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-cl2wqye","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-cl2wqye","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"苏轼对曹操的评价，结合“然天下终于分裂，讫魏之世，而不能一。盖尝试论之。魏武长于料事，而不长于料人”“知之而不能权之以人，则亦纷纷焉或胜或负，争为雄强，而未见其能一也”可知，苏轼认为曹操不是“大智者”，他不能准确地权衡对手，未能统一天下。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-cywl6ki","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-cywl6ki","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"朱敬则对曹操的评价，结合“观曹公明锐权略，神变不穷，兵折而意不衰，在危而听不惑，临事决机，举无遗悔，近古以来，未之有也”“然天下精明之士，拓落之材，趋若百川之崇巨海，游尘之集高岳。故有荀彧、郭嘉等，或敛风长感，或一见尽怀。然后览英雄之心，骋熊罴之勇，挟天子以崇大顺，扶幼主而显至公，武功赫然，霸业成矣”可知，朱敬则高度肯定了曹操的功业，认为曹操有谋略，善决断，意志坚定，以至吸引贤才归附，成就霸业。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-x98nuq5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-x98nuq5","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"参考译文："}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-sd8isnt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-sd8isnt","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"世人所说的智者，能知道天下的利与害，能审察计谋的得与失，如此而已。这样的智慧，也有不能应付的时候。只做有利的事，不做有害的事，在有的时候就会无计可施，也不会尽得天下之利。古人所说的有大智慧的人，他们既知道利害得失的计谋，又能根据人的特点来进行斟酌使用。因此有时敢做天下极其危险的事，而能终于成就大功，这就是根据人的特点来使用计谋。轻视敌人会导致失败，过于看重敌人往往又丧失成功的机会。为什么呢？因为天下没有万无一失的利益，做事情总想着万无一失，必然会影响成功。所以，知道我如何战胜别人，而别人不知道如何战胜我，这种人没有谁能战胜他。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-j9r58jo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-j9r58jo","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当汉室衰微，豪杰并起，争夺天下，二袁、董卓、吕布，争相攻杀，而孙权、刘备，又屈居在一个角落里，他们在用兵取胜方面，当然无法和曹氏抗衡，然而天下终于四分五裂，一直到曹魏结束，也未能统一。就这件事，试着发表点意见。魏武帝擅长分析判断事，却不擅长分析判断人。刘备有盖世的才能，却没有应付突发事件的机智。当他刚刚打败刘璋，占领益州的时候，蜀人没有完全归附，一日有四五次哗变，斩杀也无法控制局面。放弃这个机会不攻取他，后来就发展到不敢加兵攻打的地步，一直到死都是这种情况。孙权英勇而有谋略，这就不能依靠人多势众来攻取他。魏武帝不利用中原地区的优势，却用水军与孙权一决雌雄，一日一夜行军三百里前去争利。魏武帝犯了两个会导致失败的错误来攻打孙权，所以在赤壁损兵折将，而使东吴强大起来。攻取刘备贵在神速，不应该放长线。当蜀人不信任他，民心未附的时候，卷起铠甲快速追赶他，虽然犯兵家大忌，也可以达到目的。孙权，应以计谋巧取，不能用人多势众来强攻，想用刚刚投降的荆州士兵，乘胜拿下孙权。魏武帝不是不知道这件事难，只是寄希望于侥幸孙权不敢抵抗。这种做法，用在刘备刚刚占领的西蜀，可以取得成功。所以说，魏武帝在攻打刘备这件事上过于谨慎，丧失了成功的机会，在攻打孙权时过于草率，从而导致失败。这不就是擅长分析判断事却不擅长分析判断人的过失吗？"}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-m13sy8d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-m13sy8d","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"唉！事情的利与害，计谋的得与失，天下有才能的人都能知道。但仅仅知道这个，不能根据人的特点来斟酌使用，所以魏武帝有时胜，有时败，争雄一生，却没有看到他统一天下。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-u9bw9nf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-u9bw9nf","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（宋·苏轼《魏武帝论》，有删节）"}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-u6nokpn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-u6nokpn","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"看曹公聪明睿智擅长权力谋略，神机妙算变化无穷，虽然打了败仗，意气却丝毫不衰微，处在危险的境地可是视听一点都不受蒙蔽，面对大事决定战机，只要行动就没有遗漏和后悔的，近古以来，没有这样的人才。虽然名声不大，兵力不强，地方狭小，实力弱小，官渡之战中受困，濮阳一战失败。然而天下精明的士人，落魄的才子，奔向曹公就像百川归向大海，漂浮的尘土向高高的山峰聚集一样。所以有荀彧、郭嘉等，或是被他的风采感动，或是对他一见倾心。然后获得英雄之心，驾驭熊罴之勇，挟持天子来使得国家顺遂，扶持幼主而彰显显至公，功业显赫，霸业就完成了。"}]},{"ID":"20260605111925-a2n2oln","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605111925-a2n2oln","updated":"20260605111925"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（唐·朱敬则《魏武帝论》，有删节）"}]}]}